                            <comment id="13187539" author="mgrigorov" created="Tue, 17 Jan 2012 09:04:38 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;A patch that fixes the problem.&lt;br/&gt;
It moves the check for &quot;isActionAuthorized(RENDER)&quot; to Page#onConfigure() instead of #onBeforeRender() because the latter is not called anymore in such cases.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Igor, please review.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13187540" author="papegaaij" created="Tue, 17 Jan 2012 09:05:58 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Probably applies to 1.4 as well. I did not test it on 1.4, but the patch for &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/WICKET-4256&quot; title=&quot;onBeforeRender() is called on components that are not allowed to render&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;WICKET-4256&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;WICKET-4256&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; got backported to 1.4.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13188101" author="ivaynberg" created="Tue, 17 Jan 2012 22:54:49 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;blah. 1.5.x fix is committed under &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/WICKET-4030&quot; title=&quot;HeaderResponse.renderCSSReference does not render context path relative url, but wicket filter url-pattern relative url&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;WICKET-4030&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;WICKET-4030&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; by mistake :/&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13188112" author="ivaynberg" created="Tue, 17 Jan 2012 23:08:25 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;added the test to 1.4.x, it does not suffer from this problem.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
